
  This directory contains the code for 3 executables:

  =====================================================================
  sr2gr - converts slant range imagery into ground range imagery
	
	Usage: sr2gr infile outfile pix_code [-r]

	       infile     base name (.img,.ddr,.L)
	       outfile    base name (.img,.ddr)
	       pix_code   output pixel spacing code [0-8]
	                     spacing = 6.25 * 2 ^ <pix_code>
		             (eg. pix_code 4 => resolution = 100.0m)
	       -r         Use RAMP inputs; default is AISP
	
	ASF Step Tools - Version 2.00

  =====================================================================
  deskew - removes squint induced skew from an image
	
	Usage: deskew infile outfile meta

       		infile   input file name (.img,.ddr)
       		outfile  output file name (.img,.ddr)
       		meta     metadata type (0 - CEOS, 1 - AISP)

	ASF Step Tools, Version 1.10


  =====================================================================
  ui2byte - converts ASF RAMP product into byte (slant range) image

	Usage: ui2byte infile outfile
	       infile     base name (.L,.D)
	       outfile    base name (.img,.ddr)
	
	ASF Step Tools - Version 1.00

  =====================================================================

	These executables rely on routines found in asf_sar.a,
	asf_las.a, caplib.a, and geolocate.a

  =====================================================================

